description:
In his message, “Jesus, the Leper, and YOU,” Steve Wohlberg explains Matthew 8:1-4, offers hope to us all, and reveals personal details about how God has recently rescued him from one of the most horrible trials of his life. May the name of Jesus Christ be praised!
